{"thag16.8:0.1":"Theragatha 16.8 ","thag16.8:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.8:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.8:0.4":"Angulimalattheragatha ","thag16.8:1.1":"“Gaccham vadesi samanatthitomhi, ","thag16.8:1.2":"Mamanca brusi thitamatthitoti; ","thag16.8:1.3":"Pucchami tam samana etamattham, ","thag16.8:1.4":"‘Katham thito tvam ahamatthitomhi’”. ","thag16.8:2.1":"“Thito aham angulimala sabbada, ","thag16.8:2.2":"Sabbesu bhutesu nidhaya dandam; ","thag16.8:2.3":"Tuvanca panesu asannatosi, ","thag16.8:2.4":"Tasma thitoham tuvamatthitosi”. ","thag16.8:3.1":"“Cirassam vata me mahito mahesi, ","thag16.8:3.2":"Mahavanam samano paccapadi; ","thag16.8:3.3":"Soham cajissami sahassapapam, ","thag16.8:3.4":"Sutvana gatham tava dhammayuttam”. ","thag16.8:4.1":"Icceva coro asimavudhanca, ","thag16.8:4.2":"Sobbhe papate narake anvakasi; ","thag16.8:4.3":"Avandi coro sugatassa pade, ","thag16.8:4.4":"Tattheva pabbajjamayaci buddham. ","thag16.8:5.1":"Buddho ca kho karuniko mahesi, ","thag16.8:5.2":"Yo sattha lokassa sadevakassa; ","thag16.8:5.3":"“Tamehi bhikkhu”ti tada avoca, ","thag16.8:5.4":"Eseva tassa ahu bhikkhubhavo. ","thag16.8:6.1":"“Yo ca pubbe pamajjitva, ","thag16.8:6.2":"paccha so nappamajjati; ","thag16.8:6.3":"Somam lokam pabhaseti, ","thag16.8:6.4":"abbha muttova candima. ","thag16.8:7.1":"Yassa papam katam kammam, ","thag16.8:7.2":"kusalena pidhiyati; ","thag16.8:7.3":"Somam lokam pabhaseti, ","thag16.8:7.4":"abbha muttova candima. ","thag16.8:8.1":"Yo have daharo bhikkhu, ","thag16.8:8.2":"yunjati buddhasasane; ","thag16.8:8.3":"Somam lokam pabhaseti, ","thag16.8:8.4":"abbha muttova candima. ","thag16.8:9.1":"Disapi me dhammakatham sunantu, ","thag16.8:9.2":"Disapi me yunjantu buddhasasane; ","thag16.8:9.3":"Disapi me te manuje bhajantu, ","thag16.8:9.4":"Ye dhammamevadapayanti santo. ","thag16.8:10.1":"Disa hi me khantivadanam, ","thag16.8:10.2":"avirodhappasamsinam; ","thag16.8:10.3":"Sunantu dhammam kalena, ","thag16.8:10.4":"tanca anuvidhiyantu. ","thag16.8:11.1":"Na hi jatu so mamam himse, ","thag16.8:11.2":"annam va pana kincanam; ","thag16.8:11.3":"Pappuyya paramam santim, ","thag16.8:11.4":"rakkheyya tasathavare. ","thag16.8:12.1":"Udakanhi nayanti nettika, ","thag16.8:12.2":"Usukara namayanti tejanam; ","thag16.8:12.3":"Darum namayanti tacchaka, ","thag16.8:12.4":"Attanam damayanti pandita. ","thag16.8:13.1":"Dandeneke damayanti, ","thag16.8:13.2":"ankusebhi kasahi ca; ","thag16.8:13.3":"Adandena asatthena, ","thag16.8:13.4":"aham dantomhi tadina. ","thag16.8:14.1":"‘Ahimsako’ti me namam, ","thag16.8:14.2":"himsakassa pure sato; ","thag16.8:14.3":"Ajjaham saccanamomhi, ","thag16.8:14.4":"na nam himsami kincanam. ","thag16.8:15.1":"Coro aham pure asim, ","thag16.8:15.2":"angulimaloti vissuto; ","thag16.8:15.3":"Vuyhamano mahoghena, ","thag16.8:15.4":"buddham saranamagamam. ","thag16.8:16.1":"Lohitapani pure asim, ","thag16.8:16.2":"angulimaloti vissuto; ","thag16.8:16.3":"Saranagamanam passa, ","thag16.8:16.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thag16.8:17.1":"Tadisam kammam katvana, ","thag16.8:17.2":"bahum duggatigaminam; ","thag16.8:17.3":"Phuttho kammavipakena, ","thag16.8:17.4":"anano bhunjami bhojanam. ","thag16.8:18.1":"Pamadamanuyunjanti, ","thag16.8:18.2":"bala dummedhino jana; ","thag16.8:18.3":"Appamadanca medhavi, ","thag16.8:18.4":"dhanam setthamva rakkhati. ","thag16.8:19.1":"Ma pamadamanuyunjetha, ","thag16.8:19.2":"ma kamaratisanthavam; ","thag16.8:19.3":"Appamatto hi jhayanto, ","thag16.8:19.4":"pappoti paramam sukham. ","thag16.8:20.1":"Svagatam napagatam, ","thag16.8:20.2":"netam dummantitam mama; ","thag16.8:20.3":"Savibhattesu dhammesu, ","thag16.8:20.4":"yam settham tadupagamam. ","thag16.8:21.1":"Svagatam napagatam, ","thag16.8:21.2":"netam dummantitam mama; ","thag16.8:21.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag16.8:21.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thag16.8:22.1":"Aranne rukkhamule va, ","thag16.8:22.2":"pabbatesu guhasu va; ","thag16.8:22.3":"Tattha tattheva atthasim, ","thag16.8:22.4":"ubbiggamanaso tada. ","thag16.8:23.1":"Sukham sayami thayami, ","thag16.8:23.2":"sukham kappemi jivitam; ","thag16.8:23.3":"Ahatthapaso marassa, ","thag16.8:23.4":"aho satthanukampito. ","thag16.8:24.1":"Brahmajacco pure asim, ","thag16.8:24.2":"udicco ubhato ahu; ","thag16.8:24.3":"Sojja putto sugatassa, ","thag16.8:24.4":"dhammarajassa satthuno. ","thag16.8:25.1":"Vitatanho anadano, ","thag16.8:25.2":"guttadvaro susamvuto; ","thag16.8:25.3":"Aghamulam vadhitvana, ","thag16.8:25.4":"patto me asavakkhayo. ","thag16.8:26.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag16.8:26.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thag16.8:26.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thag16.8:26.4":"bhavanetti samuhata”ti. ","thag16.8:26.5":"… Angulimalo thero …. "}